<p>9 kai idou autoV ercetai anabathV sunwridoV kai apokriqeiV eipen peptwken Babulwn kai panta ta agalmata authV kai ta ceiropoihta authV sunetribhsan eiV thn ghn</p>
<p>10 akousate oi kataleleimmenoi kai oi odunwmenoi akousate a hkousa para kuriou sabawq o qeoV tou Israhl anhggeilen hmin</p>
