<p>15 dia to plhqoV twn feugontwn kai dia to plhqoV twn planwmenwn kai dia to plhqoV thV macairaV kai dia to plhqoV twn toxeumatwn twn diatetamenwn kai dia to plhqoV twn peptwkotwn en tw polemw</p>
