<h2>25</h2>

<p>1 kurie o qeoV mou doxasw se umnhsw to onoma sou oti epoihsaV qaumasta pragmata boulhn arcaian alhqinhn genoito kurie</p>
<p>2 oti eqhkaV poleiV eiV cwma poleiV ocuraV tou pesein autwn ta qemelia twn asebwn poliV eiV ton aiwna ou mh oikodomhqh</p>
