<h2>26</h2>

<p>1 th hmera ekeinh asontai to asma touto epi ghV Iouda legonteV idou poliV ocura kai swthrion hmwn qhsei teicoV kai periteicoV</p>
<p>2 anoixate pulaV eiselqatw laoV fulasswn dikaiosunhn kai fulasswn alhqeian</p>
