<h2>27</h2>

<p>1 th hmera ekeinh epaxei o qeoV thn macairan thn agian kai thn megalhn kai thn iscuran epi ton drakonta ofin feugonta epi ton drakonta ofin skolion kai anelei ton drakonta</p>
<p>2 th hmera ekeinh ampelwn kaloV epiqumhma exarcein kat authV</p>
<p>3 egw poliV iscura poliV poliorkoumenh mathn potiw authn alwsetai gar nuktoV hmeraV de peseitai to teicoV</p>
<p>4 ouk estin h ouk epelabeto authV tiV me qhsei fulassein kalamhn en agrw dia thn polemian tauthn hqethka authn toinun dia touto epoihsen kurioV o qeoV panta osa sunetaxen katakekaumai</p>
<p>5 bohsontai oi enoikounteV en auth poihswmen eirhnhn autw poihswmen eirhnhn</p>
<p>6 oi ercomenoi tekna Iakwb blasthsei kai exanqhsei Israhl kai emplhsqhsetai h oikoumenh tou karpou autou</p>
