<p>22 kai umeiV mh eufranqeihte mhde iscusatwsan umwn oi desmoi dioti suntetelesmena kai suntetmhmena pragmata hkousa para kuriou sabawq a poihsei epi pasan thn ghn</p>
<p>23 enwtizesqe kai akouete thV fwnhV mou prosecete kai akouete touV logouV mou</p>
<p>24 mh olhn thn hmeran mellei o arotriwn arotrian h sporon proetoimasei prin ergasasqai thn ghn</p>
<p>25 ouc otan omalish authV to proswpon tote speirei mikron melanqion kai kuminon kai palin speirei puron kai kriqhn kai zean en toiV orioiV sou</p>
<p>26 kai paideuqhsh krimati qeou sou kai eufranqhsh</p>
<p>27 ou gar meta sklhrothtoV kaqairetai to melanqion oude trocoV amaxhV periaxei epi to kuminon alla rabdw ektinassetai to melanqion to de kuminon</p>
