<p>9 oti laoV apeiqhV estin uioi yeudeiV oi ouk hboulonto akouein ton nomon tou qeou</p>
<p>10 oi legonteV toiV profhtaiV mh anaggellete hmin kai toiV ta oramata orwsin mh laleite hmin alla hmin laleite kai anaggellete hmin eteran planhsin</p>
